524
00:32:45.630 --> 00:32:47.930
Saya rasa, dia juga pergi ke Moojin selama beberapa kali.

525
00:32:50.000 --> 00:32:51.170
"Moojin"?

526
00:32:51.170 --> 00:32:53.840
Ya, apa kira-kira Anda tahu soal apa itu?

