00:33:42.550 --> 00:33:45.360
<i>Bagaimana rasanya menjadi seorang residen? 
Berat, 'kan?</i>

544
00:33:45.360 --> 00:33:48.830
<i>Ah, tidak. Aku baik-baik saja.</i>

545
00:33:50.130 --> 00:33:51.560
<i>Aey, sebentar.</i>

546
00:33:58.070 --> 00:33:59.270
<i>Halo?</i>

547
00:34:00.370 --> 00:34:01.940
<i>Ah, Moo Gang-ah. Sedang apa kalian?</i>

548
00:34:02.570 --> 00:34:05.940
<i>Ah, begitu? Ibu akan segera ke sana setelah selesai seminar.</i>

549
00:34:05.940 --> 00:34:07.210
<i>Jadi, bersenang-senanglah dengan kak--</i>

550
00:34:09.610 --> 00:34:11.380
<i>Ah, sebentar.</i>

551
00:34:11.680 --> 00:34:13.920
<i>Ajak kakakkmu berkeliling Moojin.</i>

552
00:34:14.050 --> 00:34:15.490
<i>Sampai jumpa nanti.</i>

553
00:34:16.760 --> 00:34:18.760
<i>Sebentar, apa yang terjadi?</i>

