Di mana Dokter min? Kurasa ini serangan jantung.

929
00:57:38.070 --> 00:57:39.980
- Siapkan defibrillator... 
- Dokter, ini serangkan jantung.

930
00:57:39.980 --> 00:57:41.040
Minggir!

931
00:57:46.920 --> 00:57:48.620
- Begitu?
- Ya.

932
00:57:48.620 --> 00:57:51.720
Tilang kecepatannya tepat pada hari insiden itu.

933
00:57:52.790 --> 00:57:54.520
<i>Apa? 120 ribu won?</i>

934
00:57:54.520 --> 00:57:57.290
"14 Oktober, Persimpangan Gangjeong."

935
00:57:58.230 --> 00:58:00.230
"140 km per jam"?

936
00:58:01.300 --> 00:58:02.960
Tapi, persimpangan Gangjeong...

937
00:58:02.960 --> 00:58:05.600
...ada di arah berlawanan dari <i>shopping mall</i> itu.

938
00:58:05.600 --> 00:58:07.540
Dia pamit pergi ke<i> shopping mall,</i>

939
00:58:07.540 --> 00:58:09.640
